{"tid":386842,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"17歲逆子嫌買錯飲品　拐杖打到父母逃落樓","createTime":"2017-09-04T07:56:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-03T12:18:29.000Z","uid":86402,"like":84,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"f73331f2da2f3e346ea8873c74d43d9559ab93c3","tid":386842,"uid":86402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T07:56:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170904/mobile/bkn-20170904015252662-0904_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170904%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20170904015252662-0904_00822_001.html&d=yi%2F7EqKC%2F1bKY62EeZaE8o9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=578e7128\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170904/mobile/bkn-20170904015252662-0904_00822_001.html</a><br />\n沙田發生逆子毆打父母事件。消息指，昨晚11時許，博泉街水泉澳邨嶺泉樓一名83歲姓楊老翁，替其17歲兒子買飯，回到家卻被嫌棄飲品冷熱出錯，兒子與其老父及姓黃(54歲)的母親發生激烈爭吵。期間，逆子情緒激動，不但喝罵父母，更出手以老父的枴杖毆打兩老，兩老分別頭及手受傷，負傷逃出屋外，並到樓下大堂向當值保安求助，由保安代為報案。 <br />\n<br />\n警員接報到場，以涉嫌襲擊致造成身體實際傷害將少年拘捕，案件交由沙田警區刑事調查隊跟進。兩名傷者由救護車送院治理。"},{"pid":"d696bac18a8d775a06c11ac13410f750fddd5602","tid":386842,"uid":29167,"like":127,"dislike":0,"score":127,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T07:58:08.000Z","msg":"買錯ps4 嗰個小朋友大個喇？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d7fa495044ec81fb30032ccf15e7afcfb54d811","tid":386842,"uid":392,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T07:58:39.000Z","msg":"父親買錯psp被毆"},{"pid":"1d0080d00f0aac655c805a1dd4acedbc0173bd0e","tid":386842,"uid":53666,"like":1,"dislike":11,"score":-10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T07:59:10.000Z","msg":"抵死喎"},{"pid":"ef56c1771c8c0d06aaa50e44e65397f4f5dd32da","tid":386842,"uid":32818,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T07:59:21.000Z","msg":"法國麵包呢"},{"pid":"e49c7c48c21330a56ebc3aba98ae471ce72f58be","tid":386842,"uid":49163,"like":68,"dislike":1,"score":67,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T08:00:16.000Z","msg":"係咪佢架個仔<img src=